		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守望者钻入地面，随后突出给玩家一个环抱，造成<span color="#bababa">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="425" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守望者进行3段的普通攻击：砸、划、翻，每段分别造成<span color="#bababa">50%,80%,90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="422" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守望者将前肢插入地面，在玩家处冒出四个肢条，分别进行交砸，造成<span color="#bababa">70%,<br/>35%,7%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="739" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守望者进行连续三下的原地震敲攻击，三段分别造成<span color="#bababa">70%,70%,90%</span><span>伤害，并且前两段的每段均产生数十个随机翻滚的刺球，接触造成</span><span color="#bababa">70%,35%,7%</span><span>伤害，第三段震敲则变为产生大型的刺球，接触造成</span><span color="#bababa">80%,40%,8%</span><span>伤害。每次攻击都有概率产生2个有追踪性的刺球。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/终末绿洲的守望者.assets/Image_14.png')" x="720" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
